languages.text: "Твои предсказания и есть цепь, что душит волю свободного создания. Умолкни, мон-кай".
"Your predictions are the chain that chokes the will of a free being. Be silent, mon-keigh."

languages.text: «Tus predicciones son la cadena que ahoga la voluntad de los libres. Guarda silencio, mon-keigh».
languages.original_text: "Your predictions are the chain that chokes the will of a free being. Be silent, mon-keigh."

languages.text: 「お前の予言は、自由な存在の意志を窒息させる鎖だ。黙るがいい、モン＝ケイ」
languages.original_text: "Your predictions are the chain that chokes the will of a free being. Be silent, mon-keigh."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Eure Vorhersagen sind die Kette, die den Willen eines freien Wesens erstickt. Also schweigt, Chem-Pan-Sey."
languages.original_text: "Your predictions are the chain that chokes the will of a free being. Be silent, mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: "Eure Vorhersagen sind die Kette, die den Willen eines freien Wesens erstickt. Also schweigt, Chem-Pan-Sey."

languages.text: « La chaîne qui étouffe la volonté de tous les êtres libres, ce sont vos prédictions. Taisez-vous, mon-keigh. »
languages.original_text: "Your predictions are the chain that chokes the will of a free being. Be silent, mon-keigh."

languages.text: "Öngörülerin özgür bir varlığın iradesini boğan birer zincir gibiler. Sessiz ol mon-keigh."
